In this workshop, I practiced with the help of my friend and manual laborers for two days.

The doctor provided me a booklet outlining exercises. I practice every alternate day, but in my own time. After a month, I feel stronger and energetic after every exercise.

I will work together-2050- goal is to be healthy hence strong physically.

Bertha Jorden, 77, Santa Maria

I am a beneficiary under the age of 65. As a senior, health is very important. I am glad that I could participate in the elite empowerment workshop. I am a teacher by profession and my state of health makes me work daily in betterment in my school and career. Doctor instructed me good exercises for older people even problems in sitting posture and others. I am checking with my lifestyle and diet. I will be in better health with help from Doctor and Dementia Works team.

I found the day informational, close relationships and fellowship. I hope this could benefit people in coming future. I feel so happy to be healthier with these exercises. Thanks to SKDC, SNHD and Dementia Works for making these workshops successful.

Mary Anne Degonia, 54
